metadata.name: Fungi #1
metadata.description:
The Non-Fungible Fungi collective is a kingdom of 10,100 unique 3D animated (and enchanted) Mushroom NFTs strolling through the Ethereum blockchain. Each Mushroom falls into 1 of 3 species, Magic, Mire-able and Bog Standard with Magic being the rarest and Bog Standard being the most common.

The Genesis Collection provide us with the grandfather traits and from there we have a multitude of different traits ranging in both rarity and looks which make up the 10,000 Generative Collection.
